How to use:
Base = Base TWRP for your device Target = Target TWRP you want to port
1. Browse base TWRP 2. Browse target TWRP 3. You can extract it manual and edit it manual, or Select Auto Port if you dont know or lazy for modding it 4. After that, it will build twrp automatic, so wait for it 5. After build success, try flash recovery.img
Note: Auto Port is just simple port, for more modification use manual port (extract/build manual via button)
Report bug here https://t.me/joinchat/Fykz0Uz2iSIXb8E62yRApw
